    Black Aracnia reviewd the battle quickly and freeze framed on Autofire 
and Adrax. She leaned closer to the screen and puzzled on who they were.
    "Computer, identify these two bots." She said, still puzzled.
    The computer replied, "Atuofire and Adrax. Predacon signitures. Origin 
unknown."
    Black Aracnia's jaw dropped. She thought they were dead. And, if they 
were Predacons now, mabey they could help this fraction out....
    "Computer, locate them now."
    "Whereabouts of Adrax and Autofire are unknow. Scanners last report them 
in sector 9-8.4."
    She thought for a moment. That was where Ominous Primes old stomping 
grounds were. No doubt they took shelter in his lair. Well, at least she had 
an idea of where they were now. But, now she had to deal with Megatron and 
his lacky's.
